{{Infobox university | name = Chowmuhani Government S.A College | native_name = চৌমুহনী সরকারি এস. এ কলেজ | motto = | established = {{start date|1943}} | founder = | type = Government college | students = | location = [[Noakhali]] | city = Noakhali | country = Bangladesh | campus = [[Chowmuhani]] | sports = | website = www.cgsacollege.edu.bd }} '''Chowmuhani Government S.A College''' is a public [[college]] in [[Noakhali]], [[Bangladesh]]<ref name=Background>http://www.noakhalicoll.gov.bd/contain.php?arid=1</ref> established in 1943. The college is affiliated with National University.
Choumuhany College is a prominent educational institution of Noakhali district after [[Noakhali Science & Technology University]], [[Abdul Malek Ukil Medical College, Noakhali]] and [[Noakhali Government College]]. Every year a huge number of students get chance in different prominent university after complete their [[Higher Secondary School Certificate]] (HSC) examination from here.
